<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- smʿt ṣwtk bynạdy fjryt wạkẖtbyt
 btqwl ly : ậdm ạ̹nt fyn mn ṣwtk kẖsẖyt
 kẖjlạn rby mn dẖnwby klạmk ʿṣyt
 wbḥb qlbk jyt ly wṣwtk lsh bynạdy : ( ậdm ạ̹nt fyn )4
 2- msẖ nạsy ṣwtk yạ ạ̉bwyạ byqwl ly : yạ ạbny lyh
 lmạ qrrt ạʿysẖ bʿyd bʿyd ʿn ʿynyh
 tʿbt ktyr wqlt ạ̉rjʿ ạ̉kyd hạlạqyh
 mstny rjwʿy wbdmwʿh wbṣwth lsh bynạdy : ( ạ̹bny ạ̹nt fyn )4
 3- ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb rby nạdytny bṣwtk dʿytny lyk
 ftḥt ḥḍnk wqlt ly : fy jrạḥy hạkẖbyk
 dmy hạyṭhr kl ʿywbk whạnsy̱ mạḍyk
 ạ̉nạ wạqf mstny wṣwty lsh bynạdy : ( tʿạl ạ̹ly )4
 4- ạ̉nạ jạy yạ rby whạṭyʿk twbny fạ̉twb
 ạrḥmny rby ạ̉nạ kẖạṭy ạgẖfr ly ạldẖnwb
 ḥbytny ktyr wknt hnạk ʿsẖạny mṣlwb
 ạ̉nạ ndmạn rby sạmḥny wbạrfʿ ṣwty wbạnạdy : ( rby ạ̉nạ lyk )4</lyrics>
